  <title translate="true">Flux Observations: TOB: Transport Observation Package Pane</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Flux Observations: TOB: Transport Observation Package Pane</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Flux Observations: TOB: Transport Observation Package</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> pane is on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MODFLOW_Features_Tab" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">MODFLOW Features</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This tab is used to associate an object with a flux observation in MT3DMS. &#160;The flux observations are defined in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Manage_Flux_Observations" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Manage Flow Observations</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box. To associate an object with a flux observation, the user checks the check box for the appropriate observation in the table. The user may also specify a </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Factor</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> which determines how much of the flux to include in the observation. If no </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Factor</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> is specified, it will be set to 1 meaning that all the flux will be included in the flux observation. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">See the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Manage_Flux_Observations" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Manage Flow Observations</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box for a more extensive discussion of </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Factor</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="Add_or_remove_flux_observation"/></para>
  </body>
